<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Nelson%27s_prayer_on_Victory_timber.jpg" class="image" title="Nelson's pre-battle prayer, inscribed on oak timber from HMS Victory"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/52/Nelson%27s_prayer_on_Victory_timber.jpg/180px-Nelson%27s_prayer_on_Victory_timber.jpg" width="180" height="283" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
